<div class="jumbotron">
  <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to GatorChef</h1>
  <p class="lead">Where Gators eat Great</p>
  <hr class="my-4">
  <p>GatorChef is a web application that allows students to easily make healthy and nutritional meal plans.
        Here we show different meals you can make that will give you a healthy and balanced diet while still considering any specific meal prefences and including 
        what you want to eat. It is important for studnts to maintain healthy eating habits because it can reduce the number of health risks and increase life span.
     Not only that but a healthy student is also a better learner. Research shows that eating habits and healthy behaviors are connected to academic achievement.</p>
</div>



<div class="col d-flex justify-content-center">
<div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
    <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">Sign In</h5>
        <form class="px-4 py-3">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="exampleDropdownFormEmail1">Email address</label>
                <input type="email" class="form-control" id="exampleDropdownFormEmail1" placeholder="email@example.com">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="exampleDropdownFormPassword1">Password</label>
                <input type="password" class="form-control" id="exampleDropdownFormPassword1" placeholder="Password">
            </div>
           
        </form>
			<div class="container">
				<script src="https://apis.google.com/js/platform.js" async defer></script>

				<meta name="google-signin-client_id" content="1079354915700-9l8a4q060e01ujavrh2913j01ar06gol.apps.googleusercontent.com">

				<div class="g-signin2 center" data-onsuccess="onSignIn">
					data-scope="https://www.googleapis.com/auth/plus.login"
					data-accesstype="offline"
					data-redirecturi="https://localhost:7089/Home/Explore">
				</div>
			</div>

    </div>
</div>
</div>

	

    
    

  
